name: Shrine of Nameless Stars
description: "We are made of star stuff"—continues to blow my mind, how the elements in my blood and bones were once part of stars from some part of the universe. At some point, our own sun will die, and its dust will compose life in another planet different from ours. Now I think about the unknown star that's a part of me, nameless and forgotten. If I'm made of stardust, I would love the opportunity to let them know that their dust made an artist. My dear star, I would like to name you now.
